{"tid":894494,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【龍市二期】斷供樓湧現 豪宅5折拍賣任揀","createTime":"2018-11-08T12:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T13:44:41.000Z","uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a078e7373aa274d524a62a8fe0692674ac798b93","tid":894494,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181108/large/1541678459_8505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181108%2Flarge%2F1541678459_8505.jpg&h=c2de5ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181108/large/1541678458_2f1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181108%2Flarge%2F1541678458_2f1a.jpg&h=69d30acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深圳近期湧現大量被法院查封的樓盤，有羅湖區市價1100萬人民幣﹙下同﹚的豪宅，劈價一半賣523萬元；福田區680萬元單位，亦劈價至324萬元有售。<br />\n<br />\n內地網媒「愛股票」報道，地產經紀表示，最近出現大量被迫劈價拍賣的單位，大部份是因業主斷供或企業資不抵債而被銀行追數。今年內地消費借貸大增，但整體消費額並無增加，因為很多人其實是借錢去炒樓。因此近期樓價下跌，令炒樓客脫不到手，只能繼續靠高達20厘的消費貸款供樓，雪球愈滾愈大後，終於爆煲。<br />\n<br />\n深圳政府的樓市調控繼續加強，六成的新增房屋，都要以六折甚至更低價錢出售和租賃，而華為等高科技企業因租貴搬離深圳，大量減少需求下，令深圳高樓價再支撐不住。"},{"pid":"8466e842a028d23c12c6054e53ae874b2237a887","tid":894494,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:32:37.000Z","msg":"20厘息供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03bd13605fcd546d9ae98fa58b7fd3401119557f","tid":894494,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47aa6e6f16cee91a527efb4153b7ad5e1d79e2be","tid":894494,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8939ecdb15b805b71a6dde1d9a5d4bf93e16ee8","tid":894494,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0